title: Jungler with large champ pool looking for team, active.
body:
Played over 2K normals most of which were jungle games. Never played rank except at the end of last two seasons. Played 30 games end of last season, winning 28 and landing in Gold V. Looking to be more competitive in the team setting rather then solo queue. 

 Easy going guy that isn't gonna flame cause you fked your flash. Large champion pool, play both current meta champs and compositional champs. Real active.
